# Application Detail Page

## Tab Architecture
Tab order (left to right): Job Details ‚Üí Your Fit ‚Üí Strategy ‚Üí Company ‚Üí Cover Letter ‚Üí Resume ‚Üí **Optimize CV** ‚Üí Interview ‚Üí **Mock Session** ‚Üí **Outreach**

| Tab | Pane ID | Container | Sub-tabs? |
|-----|---------|-----------|-----------|
| Job Details | `pane-jobdetails` | `#jobDetailsContent` | No |
| Your Fit | `pane-fit` | `#fitContent` | No |
| Strategy | `pane-strategy` | `#strategyContent` | No |
| Company | `pane-company` | `#companyContent` | No |
| Cover Letter | `pane-cover` | `#coverContent` | No |
| Resume | `pane-resume` | `#resumeContent` | **Yes: Overview, Experience, Keywords & ATS, Summary** |
| **Optimize CV** | `pane-optimize` | `#cvOptimizeContent` | No ‚Äî see **`cv-optimizer-feature.mdc`** |
| Interview | `pane-interview` | `#interviewContent` | Yes: Process, Questions, Preparation |
| **Mock Session** | `pane-practice` | `#mockInterviewContent` | No ‚Äî see **`mock-interview-feature.mdc`** |
| **Outreach** | `pane-outreach` | `#ho-setup` / `#ho-progress` / `#ho-results` | No ‚Äî see **`hiring-outreach-feature.mdc`** |

**First active tab is `jobdetails`** (not `company`). `pane-jobdetails` carries the `active` class in HTML. Page tab bar uses **10-column CSS grid**.

## Mock Session Tab

Conversational mock interview (HR / Pro / Manager; 10/15/20 minutes). Browser STT/TTS with typed fallback. See **`mock-interview-feature.mdc`**.

`ui/src/pages/application-detail.ts` calls `window.initMockInterviewTab(currentSessionId)` on `data-tab="practice"`.

Sections: `#mi-setup`, `#mi-active`, `#mi-results`. Setup uses flex ‚Üí require `#mi-setup.mi-setup-empty.is-hidden { display: none; }`.

UI aligns with **Optimize CV**: centered empty-state + config selects + AI Setup warning; live session uses `apply-decision-banner` + `content-section` + `regen-btn` / `cl-copy-btn`; debrief uses results banner + score chips.

## Outreach Tab

Public web contact finder + copy-only draft messages (no send integration, no professional networking profile links). See **`hiring-outreach-feature.mdc`**.

`ui/src/pages/application-detail.ts` calls `window.initHiringOutreachTab(currentSessionId)` on `data-tab="outreach"`.

Sections: `#ho-setup`, `#ho-progress`, `#ho-results` ‚Äî only one visible at a time via `.is-hidden`. **`#ho-setup.ho-setup-empty.is-hidden { display: none; }`** required when setup uses `display: flex`.

UI aligns with **Optimize CV** / **Mock Session**: centered empty-state, AI Setup warning (`#ho-ai-setup-warning`), progress spinner, contact cards with **Copy** buttons for email drafts and short messages.

## CV Optimizer Tab

Standalone on-demand feature ‚Äî **not** part of the 5-agent LangGraph workflow. Logic lives in `ui/src/pages/cv-optimizer.ts` and `ui/src/cv-optimizer/**/*.ts`; styles in `application.html` `<style>` block (`.cvo-*` classes). Full export + loop details: **`cv-optimizer-feature.mdc`**.

`ui/src/pages/application-detail.ts` calls `window.initCvOptimizerTab(currentSessionId)` when the user switches to `data-tab="optimize"`.

State sections inside `#cvOptimizeContent`: `#cvo-setup`, `#cvo-progress`, `#cvo-results` ‚Äî only one visible at a time via `.is-hidden`. **`#cvo-setup.cvo-setup-empty.is-hidden { display: none; }`** required (setup uses `display: flex`; global `.is-hidden` alone is insufficient).

Setup UI matches Cover Letter / Resume empty states (centered icon, `empty-state-title`, `regen-btn`). Shared empty-state layout tokens in `:root`: `--tab-empty-padding-x`, `--tab-empty-min-height`.

| `data-action` | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `startCvOptimization` | POST `/api/v1/cv-optimizer/{session_id}/start` ‚Äî hides setup, shows progress |
| `clearCvOptimization` | DELETE result, return to setup |
| `copyOptimizedCv` / `copyCvoCoverLetter` | Clipboard |
| `downloadOptimizedCvOdt` | GET `/download-cv` ‚Äî 429/`RATE_4001` ‚Üí toast, not markdown fallback |

Score chart bars: **`data-score`** attribute + JS width assignment ‚Äî never inline `style="width: ‚Ä¶"` in template strings (CSP).

## Generate Resume Tips / Cover Letter (analysis_complete)

`generateSingle('cover'|'resume', btn)` in `ui/src/pages/application-detail.ts` POSTs to `/workflow/regenerate-cover-letter` or `/workflow/regenerate-resume`.

**On any failure (429, quota, other):** show toast (`formatWorkflowFailureDetail` / `apiErrorMessage`), restore **empty-state UI** (photo-2 screen) ‚Äî **never** render agent error blobs in tab content.

Resume empty state: `_renderResumeTipsEmptyState()`. Treat missing or failed data via `_resumeTipsHasFailure(resume)` ‚Äî checks `resume.error`, `comprehensive_advice.error`, and `parse_error`.

Backend: `POST /workflow/regenerate-resume` calls `_raise_if_agent_soft_failure()` in `api/workflow.py` before commit ‚Äî agent fallback JSON with `comprehensive_advice.error` becomes **429/503**, not persisted partial tips.

