## Company Tab ‚Äî Data Field Mapping
Source: `company` object from `CompanyResearchResult`. If `job.company_name` is empty or passes **`isPlaceholderCompanyName()`**, the main heading still follows the **About this opportunity** pattern above; show research notices from `research_quality` / staffing when present. The rest of the tab renders normal company research output (unnamed-posting / job-context research from the backend).

| Section | Fields |
|---------|--------|
| Stats bar | `company_size`, `founded`, `website` (only rendered when value starts with `http://` or `https://`), `industry`, `hiring_timeline` (appended with `(estimated)`) |
| Mission & Vision | `mission_statement`, `vision` |
| Key Products & Services | `key_products: List[str]` |
| Values | `core_values: List[str]` ‚Äî `"Name: description"` ‚Üí cards |
| Workplace Culture | `work_environment`, `remote_work_policy`, `diversity_inclusion` |
| Leadership | `key_leadership: List[{name, title, background}]` ‚Äî `.leader-title` in muted color |
| Benefits | `employee_benefits: List[str]` |
| Market Context | `competitors`, `market_position`, `competitive_advantages`, `growth_opportunities`, `recent_developments` |
| Recent Developments | Shown with `company.research_date` as "as of [Date]" |
| What They Look For | `what_to_emphasize: List[str]` |
| How to Show Culture Fit | `how_to_show_culture_fit: List[str]` |
| Things to Be Aware Of | `red_flags_to_watch: List[str]` ‚Äî amber (not red) warning style |

### Company Website URL Validation
Before rendering the `website` stat link, validate it:
```javascript
const _rawWebsite = company.website || '';
const _validWebsite = /^https?:\/\//i.test(_rawWebsite) ? _rawWebsite : '';
// Only render the stat block if _validWebsite is non-empty
```
LLMs sometimes return `"Unknown"`, `"N/A"`, or other non-URL strings. Rendering these as `<a href="Unknown">` creates relative links that navigate away from the app and show an error page. Silently hiding the stat is the correct behaviour when no valid URL is present.

