```
.apply-decision-banner / .apply-good / .apply-review / .apply-poor / .apply-muted
.percentile-track (position: relative, no overflow: hidden) / .percentile-marker (animated dot, position set via JS)
.breakdown-na              "N/A" salary text style
.skill-gap-note / .mitigation-tip / .competitive-card
